      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an investment-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six power plant. The engine maintains factory-spec compression and has received a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul to ensure precise variable valve timing. The longitudinal chassis is in impeccable state, featuring a professionally reinforced rear subframe to maintain torsional rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is transmitted through a tactile Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. The suspension bushings and dampers are in peak condition, preserving the communicative steering rack feedback. With flawless factory paint and a cabin free of any bolster wear or pixel degradation, this vehicle is a mechanically superior example of the naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
